[{"question":"From what you understand of what the president will be revealing tomorrow, as what he wants to push forward with, is that enough?","answer":"It is a fantastic start, Piers.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":36,"aSentId":37},{"question":"Can it actually become law?","answer":"Well, that remains to be seen.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":78,"aSentId":79},{"question":"Is it as shocking as many would have us believe?","answer":"Yes, it is.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":103,"aSentId":104},{"question":"Will they just go and find some other weapon that can do the same job for them?","answer":"Well, this is like Sandy Hook certainly to motivate us to do some reasonable, sensible things that we -- that we must do about gun violence.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":111,"aSentId":112},{"question":"How do you deal with the Americans who say, no, you\u0027re not having any of my guns, it\u0027s my Second Amendment right to bear arms, I can have all this?","answer":"Well, first of all, no one is talking about taking anyone\u0027s weapon.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":128,"aSentId":129},{"question":"Well, that\u0027s not good enough anymore, is it?","answer":"Well, listen, I agree with you.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":151,"aSentId":152},{"question":"Dr. Fox, do you want to jump in here?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":189,"aSentId":190},{"question":"Why is that?","answer":"Well, because evil is going to happen.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":220,"aSentId":221},{"question":"Where do we draw the line?","answer":"But the First Amendment refers to the freedom of expression, on speech and for the press.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":229,"aSentId":230},{"question":"Why -- why ban machine guns then?","answer":"Machine guns were banned in 1934 as a result of the National Firearms Act.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":239,"aSentId":240},{"question":"What does that tell you about -- as a reaction to Aurora and then Sandy Hook?","answer":"Well, Piers, look, the reality is, is that gun sales sigh rocketed upon the election of Barack Obama and Vice President Joe Biden in 2009.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":291,"aSentId":292},{"question":"When you hear people say there\u0027s just no comparison between, say, the M-16 military weapon and an AR- 15, what is your reaction?","answer":"Well, I understand what his position is and it\u0027s a little bit of semantics.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":312,"aSentId":313},{"question":"What does any civilian need one?","answer":"To protect myself and protect my family.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":337,"aSentId":338},{"question":"You believe that an American government in the modern age is going to turn tyrannical?","answer":"No, I\u0027m not saying --","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":345,"aSentId":346},{"question":"That you would need an AR-15 to protect yourself against your own government?","answer":"Well, let\u0027s look at it right now.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":350,"aSentId":351},{"question":"Government\u0027s monopoly on violence?","answer":"No, the government has a monopoly on legitimate violence.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":407,"aSentId":408},{"question":"To have an AR-15?","answer":"To have any gun.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":423,"aSentId":424},{"question":"Why do you need an AR-15?","answer":"Because I do want to protect my family.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":425,"aSentId":426},{"question":"What else do you call it?","answer":"You and I agree.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":464,"aSentId":465},{"question":"The question is, how many would if they didn\u0027t have guns in their homes?","answer":"They would find something else.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":515,"aSentId":516},{"question":"How do you convince them this is not an attack on their rights, if you like?","answer":"It is not an attack on their rights.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":525,"aSentId":526},{"question":"I mean, how are you going to tell my children that nothing has been done after what happened to our family?","answer":"But, Piers, the truth of the matter is this.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":567,"aSentId":568},{"question":"When you have a family like this who has been destroyed over what has happened -- you saw, Ashley -- Kendra, when you hear people try to just insist on saying these AR-15 weapons are not assault weapon, what do you say to that?","answer":"It\u0027s really impossible for me to understand that the killers could get that kind of power in their hands.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":576,"aSentId":577},{"question":"When you hear people talk in this way and just have no apparent comprehension, I think, of why you want these kind of weapons taken away, what is your reaction?","answer":"Well, I agree with this lady about it is our Constitutional right to have -- bear arms.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":644,"aSentId":645},{"question":"Do you think he\u0027s got it about right?","answer":"I hope to see a ban on assault rifles or much stricter possession of them.","docId":"130115pmt","qSentId":652,"aSentId":653}]